Module com.example.miniproject2
Package com.example.miniproject2.model

Class AGame

java.lang.Object
com.example.miniproject2.model.AGame
All Implemented Interfaces:
IGame
Direct Known Subclasses:
Game
public class AGame extends Object implements IGame
The AGame class is an abstract base class that defines the common interface for different types of Sudoku games. It implements the IGame interface and provides method stubs for game-related functionalities.
